{"tid":2157373,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"九龍醫院護士中招 同事隔離","createTime":"2020-08-15T03:58:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T03:58:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"daee0b5690443f9ad247ba8668865112e5bdda29","tid":2157373,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-15T03:58:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200815/NKW6KKY2DZBZLORVGH4OQIO5DI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200815%2FNKW6KKY2DZBZLORVGH4OQIO5DI%2F&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8RSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=8178f0e3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200815%2FNKW6KKY2DZBZLORVGH4OQIO5DI%2F&h=fbaacf40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200815/NKW6KKY2DZBZLORVGH4OQIO5DI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n九龍醫院護士中招 同事隔離<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/TSt-Vmw8lH_zE7jBBsCsL3hSrm0=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DLSQ66KRBBCPNEZEHLHXTQDBVM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FTSt-Vmw8lH_zE7jBBsCsL3hSrm0%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDLSQ66KRBBCPNEZEHLHXTQDBVM.jpg&h=9dc83e6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■九龍醫院一名護士初步確診，院方已消毒其工作病房。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】武漢肺炎疫情死亡人數持續上升，昨日再增一宗死亡個案，累計67名確診病人離世。醫管局昨亦公佈，一名九龍醫院骨科延續護理病房護士初步確診，該名護士8月12日早上因喉嚨痛及發燒等症狀，曾到基督教聯合醫院急症室求診，其後初步確診。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n67歲長期病患者離世<br />\n<br />\n武肺疫情持續，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局昨日亦公佈，一名九龍醫院骨科延續護理病房護士初步確診。該名護士的家人星期三確診，同日護士出現發燒及喉嚨痛等症狀，其後到聯合醫院求醫。該護士最後上班日期為星期二，有一名同事因曾一同用膳被列為緊密接觸者，兩名同事需要接受醫學監察。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局表示，已為九龍醫院延續護理病房內的24名病人以及一名相關員工進行武漢肺炎病毒測試，全部結果為陰性，醫院已為相關病房及設施消毒及清潔。<br />\n<br />\n該名初步確診護士目前在將軍澳醫院進行隔離治療，情況穩定。"}]}